{"tid":1037678,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"組團潛海岸公園　大媽狂捕海膽　揚言︰有排食","createTime":"2019-02-26T06:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T06:26:55.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc4a2b23edc16162d51feb9619da345348b11ef","tid":1037678,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>組團潛海岸公園 大媽狂捕海膽 揚言︰有排食</strong><br />\n<br />\n片LINK：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2BQl45S\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2BQl45S&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfYBs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=086c056b\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2BQl45S</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190226/photo/bkn-20190226133601094-0226_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190226140639\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190226%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190226133601094-0226_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190226140639&h=172dceb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢度海岸公園嚟㗎！<br />\n<br />\n海下灣海岸公園慘淪「美食展」。近日有港人組隊駕水上電單車到海下灣海岸公園捕捉海膽，並即場拆殼品嘗，被網民批評破壞生態環境。根據《海岸公園及海岸保護區規例》，任何人不得在海岸公園或海岸保護區內傷害、移走或帶走任何動物或植物。<br />\n<br />\n有大媽及其同行友人在網上分享在海岸公園遊玩的經歷，興奮地表示︰「今日唔行山，跟車去食海膽」。有人身穿潛水衣潛入水域，以綠色漁網袋捕捉海膽，並在貼文指︰「海下公園水底真係好多海膽，有排食」。<br />\n<br />\n照片所見，他們在海岸公園對出海面泊了多部水上電單車，又穿着潛水衣坐在石灘，將捕捉的海膽即場拆殼，有人開心自拍，並指海膽「好鮮甜」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民批評：「離晒大譜」、「海岸公園唔係養海膽畀你食」、「就係你呢啲人，海下就畀你破壞晒」、「喺海岸公園搞破壞」。<br />\n<br />\n根據本港法例《海岸公園及海岸保護區規例》，任何人不得在海岸公園或海岸保護區內以任何方式釣魚、捕魚或獵捕、傷害、移走或帶走任何動物或植物，不論活的或死的或其部分；不得在海岸公園或海岸保護區內進行滑水，包括利用滑水板、操作噴射滑橇或水上電單車。一經定罪，可處罰款25,000港元及監禁1年。"},{"pid":"1d3ba479c1599bb1bdf1c2999542e2d8196f7cf0","tid":1037678,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190226/photo/bkn-20190226133601094-0226_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190226140639\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190226%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190226133601094-0226_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190226140639&h=4f33679a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他們即場拆殼品嘗。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"888af274fa1a03c5cadd75ab6944472bdd09c251","tid":1037678,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190226/photo/bkn-20190226133601094-0226_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190226140639\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190226%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190226133601094-0226_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190226140639&h=ce1602bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子品嘗海膽時露出興奮的表情。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"b6d1ad9cc366e72361d5c41ffe9f71072e6e34b9","tid":1037678,"uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190226/photo/bkn-20190226133601094-0226_00822_001_04p.jpg?20190226140639\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190226%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190226133601094-0226_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20190226140639&h=ff0e35ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n綠色魚網袋內約有10隻海膽。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"9ef54b9ca288517a7e3e4b746a2e685f5ef94cdc","tid":1037678,"uid":113064,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:14:08.000Z","msg":"成班乞丐冇錢買海膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c63c7a39c9fa421974cacf2ef3acb94539291c","tid":1037678,"uid":144222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:14:16.000Z","msg":"冇睇過龍咁威 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89165b8c72716550a699f2122070f6f4eb9bad2c","tid":1037678,"uid":20809,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:15:15.000Z","msg":"整d假海膽入面裝屎，掉係果頭俾佢地捉"},{"pid":"e290c83e870123459fcab51abfb92